show.description: When the arrogant and wealthy Aditya Paswan returns to his hometown after years abroad, he hides his billionaire status behind a simple identity. But when he meets the fiery and independent Jhanvi, his past secrets, family wounds, and unresolved rivalries resurface. In a clash of pride, love, and redemption, Samar must choose between ego and heart before it's too late. Watch Now!
